    <briefdescription>
<para><bold> Class <computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1GF__pair" kindref="compound">GF_pair</ref></computeroutput> represents Green&apos;s functions in both time or frequency domain. </bold> </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Purpose</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
<blockquote><para>This class contains two <computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1GF" kindref="compound">GF</ref></computeroutput> data structures for representing complex matrix valued Green&apos;s functions on a time and frequency grid (retarded and lesser component), and provides a FFT function given by the helper class <computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver" kindref="compound">fft_solver</ref></computeroutput> for calculating Fourier integral transforms. </para>
</blockquote></para>
    </detaileddescription>
